{"tid":2320585,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"彭韻僖：律師會籲社會捍衛法治　指會為司法機構發聲","createTime":"2020-12-11T02:33:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T04:49:58.000Z","uid":142878,"like":6,"dislike":98,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"ebf6b8aa8920467cf55318284115e566e7333c7d","tid":2320585,"uid":142878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:33:46.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】有法官近日遭到恐嚇，律師會會長彭韻僖呼籲社會捍衛法治，又指律師會會為司法機構發聲。<br />\n<br />\n彭韻僖：「法律界的人士，不論是律師、大律師或市民，一定要捍衛法治，因為我們的法治得來不易。我們的司法機構很多時不可隨便說話，需要我們為它發聲，說出我們每人應做的事。」<br />\n<br />\n另外，律師會舉辦十周年活動，因應去年的社會運動，不少學生產生疑問和不滿，認為香港有「警暴」問題，<span class=\"red\">律師會認為不應該迴避，已聯絡七個紀律部隊，將開放予初中學生參觀，讓他們了解紀律部隊日常運作。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=416110\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416110&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqeisLzr3S4L08%2B1QJ77HZeU%3D&h=3691e9b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D416110&h=c6a6f433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=416110</a>"},{"pid":"e4bd324cb0bfc8db21a9fbafe2eda18937fc8f41","tid":2320585,"uid":11097,"like":22,"dislike":2,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:34:37.000Z","msg":"笑唔笑撚死人呀你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b96b80a16ada0ee828e289ac902a123d3568d95","tid":2320585,"uid":44209,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:35:18.000Z","msg":"律師會係垃圾中嘅垃圾，何君堯都做到前會長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"648f629eda8ff620e947e4a2604350169d4a1218","tid":2320585,"uid":11097,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T02:35:30.000Z","msg":"正常官俾藍屍